Title: 149: Data Science Tips for Startups to Large Companies
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the Associate Director of Data Science for Merck and Co., You will learn about Data Science Leadership and how to serve your team, hear about the rapidly evolving world of AI startups, and the ethical implications of Artificial Intelligence with its rapid integration in the society.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/149
